{"tid":1138264,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"人應該要點生活？","createTime":"2019-05-04T12:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T05:42:33.000Z","uid":76885,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e7d1aa1b1d6b47b0aa2652a037ae70cd81803e16","tid":1138264,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T12:01:36.000Z","msg":"唔太求成就。<br />\n唔太求物質享受。<br />\n無特別深刻既興趣。<br />\n無好鍾意好愛既野。<br />\n<br />\n道家、佛家、Stoics、尼采？Positive psychology&hellip;Psychoanalysis？<br />\n唔同既思想都有睇下&hellip;<br />\n但就無咩邊範係特別認同到，覺得跟住佢行就滿足。<br />\n<br />\n外面世界多人求成就求物質享受求愛欲關係？<br />\n有時聽到人講，就會心郁郁覺得&hellip;自己係咪應該都學佢地？<br />\n但行一步就覺，再行落去一定有好多釋同道講既Suffering。<br />\n<br />\n有無人都係唔太識生活？<br />\n或者有無人自覺好識生活，可以分享下心得？"},{"pid":"5e2d4a6c293f09cf48891cc1ead58f23c269d6f1","tid":1138264,"uid":241448,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T12:24:41.000Z","msg":"利申唔識生活<br />\n<br />\n如果你冇咁多慾望其實係好事，反正好多所謂suffering都係源於慾望。有能力可以試下做好事，姐係布施，暸解其他人既生活/煩惱都可以幫你解答返你自己既問題。"},{"pid":"cb8551e93b364c9f0647c178a7de9ead08987462","tid":1138264,"uid":58195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T14:52:09.000Z","msg":"我都唔識，同你一樣睇左好多嘢<br />\n好似全部都好有道理，但都差啲<br />\n你係唔係咁?"},{"pid":"3c4a4e92fef9a1e121e9a7e643c47287579e2946","tid":1138264,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb8551e93b364c9f0647c178a7de9ead08987462","tid":1138264,"uid":58195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T14:52:09.000Z","msg":"我都唔識，同你一樣睇左好多嘢<br />\n好似全部都好有道理，但都差啲<br />\n你係唔係咁?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T16:05:47.000Z","msg":"第二項前句係！<br />\n全部都覺講得好好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我唔知係咪覺得佢地唔夠好，定只係我唔識喺現實實行返 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04356f0a2598668924328836e15d806ae7e82369","tid":1138264,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T17:34:13.000Z","msg":"無咁多慾望咪好<br />\n唔知做咩好得閑做下義工<br />\n睇下點樣可以幫到其他人"},{"pid":"62b373c492678e422a47fec15982131853d4e999","tid":1138264,"uid":178574,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T17:38:06.000Z","msg":"反而覺得冇慾望都未必係好<br />\n有慾望有時先有推動力過每一日"},{"pid":"298122989b724512e4d5c718cac4ad3c1a0a2191","tid":1138264,"uid":198503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T17:38:31.000Z","msg":"我自己做下運動<br />\n玩下音樂<br />\n聽下歌<br />\n畫畫<br />\n儲少少figure<br />\n寫書法 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係好容易就一世<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我自己係每件事都想做得好   唔會玩做左就算<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我自己覺得佛道同我嘅motto 好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e5abcfe6423fe91a77b1b43bf12b3355fe4871f","tid":1138264,"uid":85806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T17:38:46.000Z","msg":"我試用張白紙畫個圓形出黎，然後慢慢諗自己所面對既問題，自己覺得幾好"},{"pid":"cdbebd6b0806133b7ccd13be2d27fc9dbcc58d79","tid":1138264,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e5abcfe6423fe91a77b1b43bf12b3355fe4871f","tid":1138264,"uid":85806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T17:38:46.000Z","msg":"我試用張白紙畫個圓形出黎，然後慢慢諗自己所面對既問題，自己覺得幾好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T23:44:51.000Z","msg":"點解要畫個圓形？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be1fa5e77272d62989392fe0d187d91eb4dcfb6","tid":1138264,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"298122989b724512e4d5c718cac4ad3c1a0a2191","tid":1138264,"uid":198503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T17:38:31.000Z","msg":"我自己做下運動<br />\n玩下音樂<br />\n聽下歌<br />\n畫畫<br />\n儲少少figure<br />\n寫書法 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係好容易就一世<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我自己係每件事都想做得好   唔會玩做左就算<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我自己覺得佛道同我嘅motto 好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T23:45:29.000